title: Weds Post Show (06-29-22)
itunes:title: Weds Post Show (06-29-22)
description:
Bobby starts by talking about Ariana Grande’s house getting broken into by a stalker. We get into a discussion of why people break into famous people’s homes. Bobby gives his thoughts after studying inflation and its effects. Amy thought she was scammed after buying shoes online. Bobby talks about why he’s giving away shoes on his Instagram. Raymundo had to talk to a family member about giving out his number.
